        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(gateway): clear admin scopes for backend self-pairing",
        "body": "Summary\n- Stop treating shared token/password auth as sufficient to preserve any self-declared operator scopes for local backend self-pairing.\n- Keep unscoped backend local handoff intact, while routing scoped local backend Gateway calls through normal device identity so internal loopback calls still work.\n- Add explicit issue coverage for loopback/no-Origin backend identity + shared token/password + self-declared operator scopes + no device identity.\n\nReal behavior proof\nRan a temporary local Gateway from this PR branch with token auth, then connected over loopback as `gateway-client` / `backend` using the shared token, no device identity, and a self-declared non-admin operator scope.\n\n```text\n$ OPENCLAW_STATE_DIR=/tmp/openclaw-pr86192-proof-... \\\n  OPENCLAW_CONFIG_PATH=/tmp/openclaw-pr86192-proof-.../openclaw.json \\\n  OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_PORT=39139 \\\n  OPENCLAW_GATEWAY_TOKEN=secret \\\n  node --import tsx --input-type=module\n\nlocal gateway: ws://127.0.0.1:39139\nbackend shared-token no-device requested scopes: [operator.write]\nhello auth scopes: []\nsessions.list error: missing scope: operator.read\n```\n\nThe Gateway log for the same live connection also recorded the rejected RPC:\n\n```text\n[ws] ⇄ res ✗ sessions.list 1ms errorCode=INVALID_REQUEST errorMessage=missing scope: operator.read\n```\n\nThis shows the after-fix behavior for the ClawSweeper finding: a device-less local/shared-secret backend client can no longer preserve self-declared non-admin operator scopes while skipping pairing.\n\nAdditional verification\n```text\n$ pnpm exec vitest run --config test/vitest/vitest.gateway.config.ts src/gateway/call.test.ts src/gateway/server/ws-connection/handshake-auth-helpers.test.ts src/gateway/server.auth.compat-baseline.test.ts src/gateway/server.auth.control-ui.test.ts\n\nTest Files  4 passed (4)\nTests  165 passed (165)\n\n$ pnpm exec vitest run --config test/vitest/vitest.gateway-server.config.ts src/gateway/server.sessions-send.test.ts\n\nTest Files  1 passed (1)\nTests  3 passed (3)\n\n$ pnpm exec vitest run --config test/vitest/vitest.agents.config.ts src/agents/code-mode.test.ts\n\nTest Files  1 passed (1)\nTests  30 passed (30)\n\n$ git diff --check\n# no output\n```\n\nFixes openclaw/openclaw#72418\n",
